Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, my!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasamiya's Waldenholt\Nlanded a direct hit on RM-C!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like she used her Lux\Nas a shield and blocked it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her body is unscathed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:57.07,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Tyrant's Puppet Strings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Lady Camilla\Nhad her eye on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Sasamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks are based\Non airtight projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that makes them\Nall the more easy to counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel this humiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because my master gave me\Na personality and a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have etched those words in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take you on\Nat full strength, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aha! Are we seeing\NRM-C's secret weapon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even that shallow good-for-nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has been given an absolute shield,\Na protective barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's no wonder that my master would\Nendow me with much the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This Ruin-Sharif is, so to speak,\Nthe absolute spear, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, let's compare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ruin-Sharif...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}41-type Lux, Twin Particle Cannons,\NWaldenholt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Fire!\N- Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did they annihilate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You took the words\Nright out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your swordsmanship gifts\Nare certainly terrifying, Kirin Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR-D is totally on the defensive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the Toudou Style\NConjoined Cranes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There really are no chinks\Nin that armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you're aware of this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The more I withstand the blows from\Nyour sword, the more I learn and evolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the greatest fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it won't work on you\Nif you've seen the pattern before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But a battle as one-sided as this one\Ncan be rather boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty reckless, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my body is a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have forgotten that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see I'm still in need\Nof a lot more training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I should thank you\Nfor the useful data you've given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, RM-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to unveil it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.\NYou feeble-brained moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we\Nhave to resort to that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that is my decision\Nto make, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no such authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now what did AR-D\Nmean by "it," I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, about Sasamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's hardly launched any attacks\Nin the last few minutes, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's taking time\Nto cool off that barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ruin-Sharif's rapid-fire mode is about\Nthree times as fast as the Waldenholt's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But my destructive power is greater.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Luxes my father built aren't in any way\Ninferior to those of Camilla Pareto's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm going to prove it right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a secret technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, I find it quite ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But fine. Let's test\Neach other's mettle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ruin-Sharif... maximum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Fire!\N- Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A bit too close for comfort, eh, RM-C?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you can throw up\Nthat protective barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in other areas\Nbesides your own surroundings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry, Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hold him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. You did great, Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AR-D...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what I want,\Nbut I'm going to do just as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ACM Unit, First External Armor,\Npurging all Luxes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ceding Limit Control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There they are, there they are,\Nthere they are! Oh, yes, they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Start linking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They combined?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is who I truly am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought\Nthey'd have to resort to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about throwing me for a loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a loop, you seem to be enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they have been growing up\Nat such breakneck speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing me look even more\Nimposing and commanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look way cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you're not going to attack me,\NI'll be happy to get this started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Kirin. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Anyway,\Nthat move he just made...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not what he was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The swordsmanship is the same, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,his speed and power\Nare on a whole different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think RM-C might've shared some\Nof her own Manadite with that big lunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nthen he must have some kind of defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there wasn't any problem, they could've\Njust left him the way he was until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a time limit\Nor too much of a burden on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we don't have\Nenough information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:46.06,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COOLING DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, he still needs an interval.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you buy me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your strategy meeting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was masterful. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! Never mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two are powerful enemies\Nthat have earned my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I shall destroy you\Nwith every ounce of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we just might be screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, get behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if I do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so slow to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Volnir Hammer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought\Nyou could withstand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}39-type Lux Ray Gun, Wolfdora...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you\Nto back me up, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I was before this match started,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would've concluded\Nthat your actions were futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as I am now,\NI am actually in awe of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya! Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they did\Nquite a number on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our school badges\Nhadn't been smashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we still had a lot left in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry you had to see us\Nat our most pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:06.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PHOENIX FESTA SEMIFINALS\NSAYA SASAMIYA\NAND KIRIN TOUDOU DEFEATED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't see it like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to\Navenge you in the final,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like nothing more\Nthan to do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can utter such drivel\Nafter watching our match,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're either stupid or you actually\Nthink you have a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My original goal was to achieve\Na grand slam, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would spin such a fantasy\Nunless she were stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That must be Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sasamiya, Toudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today's outcome was very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, reaching the semifinals\Nis an achievement you can be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Seidoukan's future\Nlooks much brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it wasn't anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only did it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora sure is late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed that she'd\Njoin us here after the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Dirk Eberwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Sure! Put him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you Ernesta Kuhne?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you, Tyrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what would you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you people were getting on\Nwell with the Magnum Opus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I did was agree to mutual\Nnon-interference with that crazy woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she'd never forgive you for\Nabducting the Lonely Strega, Erenshkigal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,right from under her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who cares about any of that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what I wanted to discuss...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Join forces with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How ludicrous is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you say that's a bit rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be asking this\Nafter we've gotten to know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no need for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as you help me out,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you will get the appropriate\Nprofits. That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Profits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a souvenir for you take home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can decide after seeing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's going on with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld, I take it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have the owner of this\Nterminal in my custody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Ayato Amagiri there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Flora safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your Highness! Mr. Amagiri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only knocked her unconscious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you meet my demands,\NI'll let her go right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apply for an emergency freeze\Non the Ser=Versta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember, if you turn to the police\Nor special ops organizations,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or if you withdraw from the Festa,\NI can't guarantee her safety. That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, what did he mean\Nwhen he demanded an emergency freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When its user senses danger,\Nhe can have his Ogre Lux forcefully sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it is possible\Nto disable such a seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in that event, Ayato, you'd never\Nbe able to wield the Ser=Versta again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just means that if I were to do that\Neven once, it would never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how exactly do I go about\Nputting in this request?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean\Nthat he'll really let Flora go for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But unless we do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go rescue Flora ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, there won't be any issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can feign\Nhaving accepted his demands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and rescue Flora in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put Flora's safety\Nabove all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you're willing to give up\Nwhat you want yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in protecting\Nsomething dear to you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you're going to end up sacrificing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking\Nof my own interests when I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:19:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now...\NJulis, your fear of loss is excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going through all that once\Nis more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to rescue Flora\Nand win the Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please show at least that much spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm advising you\Nnot as the student council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Letting everything go\Nthe abductor's way makes me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with Claudia's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then we'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Right.\N- Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sasamiya... listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to help\Nwhen a friend's in a jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya, Kirin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato, I want you to apply\Nfor the emergency freeze,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just as the perpetrator demanded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use my connections\Nto delay the actual process.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's an internal\NSeidoukan procedure,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APPLICATION FOR THE EMERGENCY FREEZE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it won't be easily leaked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most likely, the perpetrator forbade you\Nto withdraw from the Festa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that he could confirm\Nwhether or not you'd met his demands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So until we can confirm Flora's safety,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please keep the Ser=Versta hidden\Nand use another Lux.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since the perpetrator's targets\Nare Ayato and the Ser=Versta,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the mastermind is almost\Ncertainly Dirk Eberwein.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, Rewolf's intelligence\Nand espionage organization,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grimalkin, will be doing\Nthe actual work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can narrow down the search to their\Nterritory, the Redevelopment District.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I can only hold them off{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}until tomorrow's\Nclosing ceremony at 3 p.m.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasamiya, Toudou,\Nplease rescue Flora by then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can catch him off-guard\Nand escape,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or at least find a way\Nto contact the princess...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This power... is he a Dante?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I have no choice\Nbut to do as he says.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least for now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I can't let this end just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Not yet...\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I see there was another shooting star.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In this battle to determine\Nthe true heroine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 18\NScrambling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder how long this cycle\Nof sorrow will continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh! I sense menace!
